729464f-b.title: Richmond: Richmond Terrace - Wall Street
729464f-b.text:
Richmond Terrace, adjoining the N. W. corner of
Wall Street, showing Police Headquarters of the Borough
of Richmond. The view is north.
About 1930
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2)
The same, at a later date, from the opposite
direction.
June 13, 1937
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
